10.70	Darren_Hayman	Darren Hayman	Darren Russell Hayman (born 30 November 1970, Brentwood, Essex) is an English singer-songwriter and guitarist. He is best known as the lead singer and guitarist in Hefner. Since Hefner disbanded in 2002, Hayman has embarked on a solo career and has released five albums, three of which were with his band Darren Hayman &amp; the Secondary Modern.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4e/Darren_Hayman.jpg/250px-Darren_Hayman.jpg
